io.orchestrate.client

Class KvFetchOperation<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.orchestrate.client.KvFetchOperation<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type to deserialize the result of this operation to.

    public final class KvFetchOperation<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Fetch an object by key from the Orchestrate.io service.

    Usage: 

     KvFetchOperation<MyObject> kvFetchOp =
         new KvFetchOperation<MyObject>("myCollection", "someKey", MyObject.class);
 Future<KvObject<MyObject>> futureResult = client.execute(kvFetchOp);
 KvObject<MyObject> result = futureResult.get();
 System.out.println(result.getValue());
    See Also:
    http://java.orchestrate.io/querying/#fetch-data
